{"tid":1343470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（已剪片）議員何君堯，與元朗打人白衫兇徒勾結，始於2016年立法會新西侯選人被恐嚇","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:51:33.000Z","uid":50275,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a156dd6be4806b04b8287890f3e47437b613cc43","tid":1343470,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:49:22.000Z","msg":"（元朗白衫兇徒）議員何君堯，與元朗打人白衫兇徒勾結，2016年立法會新西侯選人被恐嚇、何君堯偷笑<br />\n<br />\n016年8月25日   有線選舉論壇<br />\n立法會新界西侯選人周永勤突然宣布棄選，因為其家人遭恐嚇，周擔心生命安危。周其後更大聲痛哭。     <br />\n<br />\n現場有人指何君堯偷笑。<br />\n_____________________<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月21日<br />\n元朗有大量白衫男子持木棍攻擊市民，<br />\n議員何君堯與白衫疑兇相識。<br />\n片段可見，何君堯與白衫疑兇握手寒暄、<br />\n何君堯向白衫疑兇道謝。<br />\n<br />\n「你係我既英雄」<br />\n白衫疑兇話：「同何議員影相呀」<br />\n_____________________<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月21日<br />\n一行數十人白衫人，於元朗站內襲擊市民<br />\n<br />\n記者亦受襲，面部流血。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ejdwx3FOC7k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEjdwx3FOC7k&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXci2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=0162ee17\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ejdwx3FOC7k</a>"},{"pid":"671c91a12ffcc058b04006fc89bbab16b2664cfc","tid":1343470,"uid":50275,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iFpFYMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiFpFYMz.png&h=5a3b140b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df00cc44423650603f6967a998f8b0ea217ce4a5","tid":1343470,"uid":50275,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rEHoWyo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrEHoWyo.png&h=78c010ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLv9R6O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLv9R6O.png&h=0891e3f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfbb4373094cf28e8f41311b298a7446a4768633","tid":1343470,"uid":54719,"like